" Some useful commands and shortcuts
"" Switch word to word
"" w - Forward with one word
"" b - Backward with one word
" Delete the parenthesis i.e. (), {},[]
"" ca[] or ca() or ca{}
" Switch to the last closed file
"" C-^ - Open the last closed file

